test_cases.comment:
Warm Up button is pressed and its verified that digout clutch neutral is activated.

Digin clutch engaged neutral is activated.

Its verified that NEUTRAL indicator is shown in green color.
test_cases.name: Warm Up - Check clutch neutral

test_cases.comment: With clutch in neutral its verified that speed demand is set to 100% when lever is at 100%.
test_cases.name: Warm Up - Full throttle ahead

test_cases.comment: With clutch in neutral its verified that speed demand is set to 0% when lever is at 0%.
test_cases.name: Warm Up - Throttle to idle

test_cases.comment: With clutch in neutral its verified that speed demand is set to 100% when lever is at -100%.
test_cases.name: Warm Up - Full throttle astern

test_cases.comment: With lever in 0% its verified that digout clutch neutral is active. With digin clutch engaged neutral its verified that operating mode is Cruise Neutral.
test_cases.name: Warm-up to Cruise Neutral

test_cases.comment: Shaft Lock signal will prevent clutch Ahead and clutch Astern.
test_cases.name: Cruise - Shaft Lock Engaged

test_cases.comment:
Lever is moved to 100%.
Its verified that digout clutch neutral signal is deactivated and that shaft brake is being disengaged.
test_cases.name: Cruise - Full throttle ahead
Cruise - Shaft brake signal fault ahead

test_cases.comment:
Lever is moved to -100%.
Its verified that digout clutch neutral signal is activated and that shaft brake is being engaged.
test_cases.name: Cruise - Full throttle astern
Cruise - Shaft brake signal fault astern

test_cases.comment: With lever in 0% its verified that digout clutch neutral is active. With digin clutch engaged neutral its verified that operating mode is Cruise Neutral.
test_cases.name: Cruise  to Trolling Neutral

test_cases.comment: Shaft Lock signal will prevent clutch Ahead and clutch Astern.
test_cases.name: Trolling - Shaft Lock Engaged

test_cases.comment:
Lever is moved to 100%.
Its verified that digout clutch neutral signal is deactivated and that shaft brake is being disengaged.
test_cases.name: Trolling - Full throttle ahead
Trolling - Shaft brake signal fault ahead

test_cases.comment:
Lever is moved to -100%.
Its verified that digout clutch neutral signal is activated and that shaft brake is being engaged.
test_cases.name: Trolling - Full throttle astern
Trolling - Shaft brake signal fault astern
